	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hi, I have a bit of info that may be helpful to those attempting this quest.  If you go to the cave and someone is already camped there, be friendly to them and offer them 5pp or so to send you a tell when they kill him, so you can time his next pop.  Then you also know the perfect time to come back to camp it.  For example, if it's getting late and you get the tell, you could log off at the camp, set your alarm, wake up early the next morning and log in to check.  The extra info is well worth the 5pp imho.<br>I got the testament last night, finally I can have my inventory slot back in my bank account!  <br><br>Hope this helps!<br><br>Kilfree<br>Shaman, 24th season<br>Tholuxe<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
